754,"uid":73565,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:11:48.000Z","msg":"以呢個閪婆掂咩衰咩既往蹟<br />\n樓價有救啦!!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ziHdn90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FziHdn90.jpg&h=fa933833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">林奠：我依家呢幾年嚟，最開心個段時刻就係2012年嘅農曆年。<br />\n<br />\n林奠：咁發生乜嘢事呢？2012年嘅農曆年我已經大致上決定退休架喇。果陣時兩個仔都仲喺英國讀緊書，<span class=\"red\">咁當然退咗休有時間咪去英國住囉</span>。<br />\n<br />\n林奠：所以<span class=\"red\">果個農曆年放咗幾日假去英國同先生就係睇樓睇吓家俬，咁就諗住有間小小嘅有前後花園嘅屋仔喺果度過返啲兩個人嘅生活</span>，但就要離兩個仔唔係好遠，因為兩個仔都喺劍橋讀書。<br />\n<br />\n林奠：<span class=\"red\">咁果段日子到今日仍然係近年最開心嘅日子</span>。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TNmx4EVX7dM&amp;t=0m19s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTNmx4EVX7dM%26t%3D0m19s&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=4ed03ec3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TNmx4EVX7dM&amp;t=0m19s</a><br />\n<br />\n林奠喺英國置業好有心得架 去英國置業嘅希望我地就交俾林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b87fafb8cac99d166c8ebca57aa79debd9ffb04","tid":2388754,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:19:15.000Z","msg":"即係食得屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711bdbd96bd13af842f571816af058e4d939207f","tid":2388754,"uid":56610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7f59d02b2fa6d551331976996ccaead0b47105f","tid":2388754,"uid":146089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:37:17.000Z","msg":"置條毛，有呢個錢移左民拉。<br />\n去接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n我有幾球係手仲留係香港托7<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}